        <num>9-10-131</num>
        <content>
          <p>All bonds taken under requirement of law in the course of a judicial proceeding may be amended and new security given if necessary.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 3434; Code 1868, § 3454; Code 1873, § 3505; Code 1882, § 3505; Civil Code 1895, § 5123; Civil Code 1910, § 5707; Code 1933, § 81-1204.)</p>
